  "riddle": "1. Seek the grand residence on the corner of Madison Avenue cherished by its illustrious owner, a tobacco magnate who dreamed of opulence. What is the name of the architect behind this mansion? \n\n2. A lineage of ambition was cultivated — how many sons filled the household of Aurora and her partner?\n\n3. In what manner do the digits of the number you just found dance in their binary attire? Count the 1-bits and unveil this mystery.\n\n4. The tale of a benefactor with an artistic vision dwells nearby. In what age did he take his final bow?\n\n5. Reflect upon the age you just discovered — what is the sum of its distinct prime factors, a treasure hidden in its composition?\n\n6. Venture forth to a canvas famed for capturing a traveler from the South Seas — which year does this artwork hail from?\n\n7. Among artistic styles, one reigns supreme; how many languages does its article speak at the summit?\n\n8. Through the hallowed halls of a renowned society bathed in history — what year marked the inception of this storied club?\n\n9. When you gaze back at your current locale, how many hospitals lie in the shadow of the coordinates frequented by the finest?\n\n10. Similar to a binary code, what is the count of 1s in the binary representation of those that protect the health of local citizens? \n\n11. The realm of real estate twinkles in names — what year did a prominent firm in this industry come into being?\n\n12. Consider that founding year: what do the distinct prime factors sum to in their elegance?\n\n13. An assemblage of commercial venues emerges; what is the typical space they command within a retail power center?\n\n14. A new era began when innovative minds reshaped shopping landscapes — when was this vision first birthed?\n\n15. What height above sea level does this modern bazaar call home?\n\n16. Behold, an arena for sport; how many stadiums stand sentinel within close proximity to retail joy?\n\n17. Combine the elevation of the wondrous shopping center with the count of nearby stadiums — what new number emerges from this union?\n\n18. In the realm of reviews, how do patrons rate this shopping paradise across the digital expanse?\n\n19. A beloved chain has spread across the nation. In how many states do their stores find solace?\n\n20. Yet another layer of altitude awaits inquiry; what is the elevation of the land where this chain flourishes?\n\n21. And in matters of health, what number of hospitals share the air with the grand store?\n\n22. Sift through the heights and health facilities of this branded haven: what is the absolute difference when you subtract the number of hospitals from the elevation you found?\n\n23. Back to the beloved chain, sum the digits of the number that represents its widespread reach.\n\n24. Recall a nostalgic brand that played in childhoods past; what year did this toy empire first open its doors?\n\n25. Also in memory's embrace, what month and year did a home goods store first grace its customers?\n\n26. A retail legend once flourished; what was the name of the mall where it chose to debut?\n\n27. A retail giant looms at Great Lakes Crossing; how high does this shopping mecca rise above sea level?\n\n28. Shoppers share their thoughts — what is the average Google rating of this vast retail strip?\n\n29. Add together the elevation of Great Lakes Crossing and its Google rating. What new value unfolds?\n\n30. In the domain of department stores, how many legal entities contributed to the legacy of this beloved brand by the 1990s?\n\n31. If you chart a course from a vibrant Manhattan district to a quaint town in Massachusetts, what is the driving distance you would cover?\n\n32. Explore an aerodrome by the sea; what is the elevation of the ground by Lancing?\n\n33. From this aviation port, sum the digits of the elevation you've unearthed.\n\n34. In a land far away, what is the current population count of the Sultan's domain?\n\n35. Out in the world of charitable endeavors, how many designations can Canada’s Revenue Agency confer upon foundations?\n\n36. Take the findings of your past few clues and compute: (clue 17 + clue 22 + clue 28 + clue 34) % 10. The result will reveal a single digit, an insight gathered from your journey.",
